{"title":"[Zinc]任务","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5111","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小明是个很好MC的人，一天，他从老郭那接了个任务，任务说明如下<br></p><p> 有N个矿洞，每发现1个矿洞关系就可以从老郭那里的到一美元，如果可以从x到y，从y能到z，那么x就可以到z；</p><p>！！需要进入B次</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行三个整数a,b,c</p><p>第二到第b+1行，每行两个整数n,m表示n和m之间的关系</p><p>第b+2到第b+2+c,每行两个整数b,l，表示询问b和l之间有没有矿洞关系</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>sum：及小明最后可以得到的money</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>   </p><pre style='font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, \"Courier New\", FontAwesome, monospace;'>6 5 3\n1 2\n1 5\n3 4\n5 2\n1 3\n1 4\n2 3\n5 6</pre><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=a,b,c&lt;=10^7</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}